==English==
===Etymology===
:from French, where mill workers would throw their wooden shoes (''sabots'') into the machinery to make it halt or break down.

===Mass noun===
#A deliberate action aimed at weakening an enemy through subversion, obstruction, disruption, and/or destruction. 

